{"tid":2092580,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"東方日報：鄭雁雄=狗官","createTime":"2020-07-03T09:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T22:59:37.000Z","uid":168774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a126713188d6b1646017a224cedfbebc0ebd3080","tid":2092580,"uid":168774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:41:56.000Z","msg":"汕尾狗官鄭雁雄擴權<br />\n<br />\n【本報綜合報道】於廣東汕尾市烏坎村風波中，曾怒斥示威村民鬧事、把境外傳媒比喻為母豬的汕尾市委書記鄭雁雄，日前當選市人大常委會主任。汕尾市委官員證實，鄭雁雄仍任汕尾市委書記。鄭因處理烏坎事件不當，遭內地網民稱呼為「狗官」，但之後竟未遭懲處，現在還集黨務和立法大權於一身，惹來網民極大憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20120111/00178_025.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20120111%2F00178_025.html&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXLhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=2f28668e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20120111/00178_025.html</a>"},{"pid":"dcbb5f73cf79b983f9aabac0dcf4cf3931354350","tid":2092580,"uid":283071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T22:59:37.000Z","msg":"其實習總點解咁重用姓鄭既人？<br />\n又係計筆劃風水野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}